* Iron Raptor looked over at Prowl, for some strange reason he didn't look well. Perhaps it was her imagination again but perhaps it wasn't, there was no harm in asking...was there?
She sighed and turned her head to look at him, if there was something wrong she wanted to know about it...perhaps she could turn that wrong into a right.*

" Are you alright?"

* What she didn't know was that he might have been in deep concentration, it was something that had slipped her mind.*
